<h2 id="announcements" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#announcements" class="header-mark"></a>Announcements</h2><p>Took a short break from game development to work on something different — a simple SaaS product!</p>
<p>I’m excited to share that <a href="https://roughtrack.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Rough Track</a> is now live! 🎉</p>
<p>Over the past two months, I’ve been prototyping a lightweight web app for creating <strong>Now–Next–Later roadmaps</strong> — a straightforward way to keep my team and stakeholders aligned.</p>]]></description>
